UNICEF aims to achieve this through Community Engagement, Social And Behaviour Change, Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Partnerships And Engagement: Public And Private, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: PROGRAMME EFFECTIVENESS

description.narrative: The CO adjusted its communication strategy and plan to reflect the new organization-wide priority as well as the direct and indirect impacts of the global COVID-19 pandemic.; The change of strategy was focused on (i) formulating new communication and advocacy tools to reach beneficiaries despite the COVID-19 social-distancing restrictions; (ii) designing appropriate messages to address both prevention of the virus and alleviate the secondary impact of the pandemic on children; and (iii) using digital platforms as important tools of mass communication and essential in COVID19 context. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:25/01/2022
